/* Answer the following: how many patients were born before the year 2060? */
SELECT
questions.response: COUNT ( DISTINCT DEMOGRAPHIC."SUBJECT_ID" ) FROM DEMOGRAPHIC WHERE DEMOGRAPHIC."DOB_YEAR" < "2060"

/* Answer the following: how many of the patients treated with main drug had a hospital stay of more than 5 days? */
SELECT COUNT ( DISTINCT DEMOGRAPHIC."SUBJECT_ID" ) FROM DEMOGRAPHIC INNER JOIN PRESCRIPTIONS on DEMOGRAPHIC.HADM_ID = PRESCRIPTIONS.HADM_ID WHERE DEMOGRAPHIC."DAYS_STAY" > "5" AND PRESCRIPTIONS."DRUG_TYPE" = "MAIN"

  "NAME" TEXT,

  "AGE" INTEGER,
  "DOB" TEXT,
  "GENDER" TEXT,
  "LANGUAGE" TEXT,
  "RELIGION" TEXT,
  "ADMISSION_TYPE" TEXT,
  "DAYS_STAY" INTEGER,
  "INSURANCE" TEXT,
  "ETHNICITY" TEXT,
  "EXPIRE_FLAG" INTEGER,
  "ADMISSION_LOCATION" TEXT,
  "DISCHARGE_LOCATION" TEXT,
  "DIAGNOSIS" TEXT,
  "DOD" TEXT,
  "DOB_YEAR" INTEGER,
  "DOD_YEAR" REAL,
  "ADMITTIME" TEXT,
  "DISCHTIME" TEXT,
  "ADMITYEAR" INTEGER
)

CREATE TABLE "DIAGNOSES" (
"SUBJECT_ID" TEXT,

/* Answer the following: what number of patients under the age of 85 had lab test named heparin,imw? */
SELECT
questions.response: COUNT ( DISTINCT DEMOGRAPHIC."SUBJECT_ID" ) FROM DEMOGRAPHIC INNER JOIN LAB on DEMOGRAPHIC.HADM_ID = LAB.HADM_ID WHERE DEMOGRAPHIC."AGE" < "85" AND LAB."LABEL" = "Heparin, LMW"

/* Answer the following: how many patients younger than 70 years have got the cerebrospinal fluid (csf) lab test done? */
SELECT
questions.response: COUNT ( DISTINCT DEMOGRAPHIC."SUBJECT_ID" ) FROM DEMOGRAPHIC INNER JOIN LAB on DEMOGRAPHIC.HADM_ID = LAB.HADM_ID WHERE DEMOGRAPHIC."AGE" < "70" AND LAB."FLUID" = "Cerebrospinal Fluid (CSF)"

/* Answer the following: get the number of patients who have pr route of drug administration and have acidosis primary disease. */
SELECT COUNT ( DISTINCT DEMOGRAPHIC."SUBJECT_ID" ) FROM DEMOGRAPHIC INNER JOIN PRESCRIPTIONS on DEMOGRAPHIC.HADM_ID = PRESCRIPTIONS.HADM_ID WHERE DEMOGRAPHIC."DIAGNOSIS" = "ACIDOSIS" AND PRESCRIPTIONS."ROUTE" = "PR"

/* Answer the following: how many patients with diagnoses icd9 code 53190 have had delta abnormal lab test status? */
SELECT
questions.response: COUNT ( DISTINCT DEMOGRAPHIC."SUBJECT_ID" ) FROM DEMOGRAPHIC INNER JOIN DIAGNOSES on DEMOGRAPHIC.HADM_ID = DIAGNOSES.HADM_ID INNER JOIN LAB on DEMOGRAPHIC.HADM_ID = LAB.HADM_ID WHERE DIAGNOSES."ICD9_CODE" = "53190" AND LAB."FLAG" = "delta"
